My first and only multigame/allinone map thanks to Poohbuhhrrr for sponsoring and influencing this work. It has 14 levels to choose from all made by me. Should run it at 66 tic sv_airaccelerate 100 or 150 and noblock. It includes ice skating, shotgun factory, bhop, race, smallcity, slide figure 8, awps, climb, dodgeball smokes, turnthatoff, touchmybox, nade preicison, scoutzknivez, 50 hp knife. Its my largest and longest map build and I won't be doing another one this large so enjoy. :)

Set for up to 64 spawns
